:Load:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/snapshot.handbook
Load

Displays a window where you can specify the
snapshot file (or other raster file) to be loaded
for viewing.

You can also load GIF format files--but these
can be saved only in raster format.

:Save:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/snapshot.handbook
Save

Displays a window where you can specify where
the snapshot file is to be saved.

Note that GIF format files can be saved only
in raster format.
		
