:LoadSaveDirectory:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/snapshot.handbook
Directory:

Name of the directory where Snapshot will store 
the output or retrieve a file.

1. Enter the directory you want. The default is 
your current working directory.

2. Enter the file name at File.

3. Click SELECT on the Load or Save button.

Note that GIF format files can be saved only
in raster format.

:LoadSaveFile:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/snapshot.handbook
