Name of the file Snapshot will store or retrieve.

Enter the file name you want. The default is
"snapshot.rs." 

Click SELECT on the Load or Save button.

Note that GIF format files can be saved only
in raster format.

:LoadSaveBut:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/snapshot.handbook
Load/Save

Once you have specified the directory and file
names, click SELECT on the Load or Save button
(toggles depending on operation you have chosen).

